snippet.title: Skeletal Dance Party - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Necromancers! Paladins! Skeletons! Monsters! Oh, my! You play as Reva, a young fox-eared necromancer who embarks on a quest to host an awesome party for all her friends… who happen to be the reanimated skeletons of her enemies.

Skeletal Dance Party (C) Catalope Games AB
